{
  "_meta": {
    "purpose": "ingame 主题统一图标清单（Asset Manifest）。业务层传语义键，asset(key,style) 解析器据此取图。",
    "game_version": "1.0",
    "source": "Pal-Windows.pak（客户端）经 texexport(CUE4Parse) 导出，见 tools/game_data/extract_ingame_icons.py",
    "generated_at": "2026-07-12",
    "path_base": "data/ingame/",
    "status_values": [
      "verified",
      "pending-extract",
      "plugin-ext",
      "plugin-ext-pending",
      "text-keep"
    ],
    "notes": [
      "ingame=游戏原生 PNG(base64 内嵌)；fantasy/pixel 用 fallback(原 Emoji/文字，保持不变)。",
      "ingame 缺失时解析器回退统一 missing 占位，绝不抛异常。",
      "元素纹理视觉顺序 00无01火02水03雷04草05暗06龙07地08冰(非枚举序，已实测)。",
      "工作纹理按图标内容绑定(非索引算术)：08=制药药瓶 09=采油油桶(与枚举相反)。",
      "server.*/plugin.* 游戏无此语义→统一插件扩展线性 SVG(data/ingame/svg/，见 tools/game_data/gen_plugin_svgs.py)，严禁套游戏图标；描边色 AssetResolver.PLUGIN_INK 临时中性暖线，待截图校准。"
    ]
  },
